=============================================================

use customize theme using sass

first create saas folder in project---
create scss file=====for ex:main.scss

main.scss
code:
$primary:#ff6347;
@import "../node_modules/bootstrap/scss/bootstrap";

//import must be last in code

install sass live extension

change setting json

add extra info

 "liveSassCompile.settings.formats":[
    {
"format": "compressed",
"extensionName": ".min.css",  ======================>file extension
"savePath": "/src/css"        ======================file path inside of source folder create css folder and inside the saas file
    }
  ]